messages.message:
Hi Brian, 
My phone broke today at the zoo and Iga is not on fb right now. Can you tell her that I am sorry for missing out on her Bday gathering tonight. I was with my nephew all day and I need to rest because my asthma is really bad. Tell her I will take her out for a birthday dinner or lunch. I hope to have a phone by Monday night, at the lastest on her birthday and I will give her a call then. Have a great night! 
-Rachel
